{"tid":2205222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[加速]关于加强新时代民营经济统战工作的意见","createTime":"2020-09-16T15:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T11:05:26.000Z","uid":119895,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95685d7c659fcbcb530df6abb60109ee4d2fdf0b","tid":2205222,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://finance.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0916/c1004-31863402.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2020%2F0916%2Fc1004-31863402.html&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=72035a53\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0916/c1004-31863402.html</a><br />\n諗起令人懷念既公私合營，今次愛國既港商都有幸加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（十）明确工作范围。统战工作要面向所有民营企业和民营经济人士，工作对象主要包括民营企业主要出资人、实际控制人，民营企业中持有股份的主要经营者，民营投资机构自然人大股东，以民营企业和民营经济人士为主体的工商领域社会团体主要负责人，相关社会服务机构主要负责人，民营中介机构主要合伙人，<strong>在内地投资的港澳工商界人士</strong>，有代表性的个体工商户。"},{"pid":"93f2b370778505252757ab1fc593db1f50341b7e","tid":2205222,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bc4ca96cfaf90aeca5b4b26a95ce12ce210d1f","tid":2205222,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"民營企業要建立黨支部，加強員工思想建設<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716827954000b8e5025441161a3acfac3b3b4a33","tid":2205222,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81bc4ca96cfaf90aeca5b4b26a95ce12ce210d1f","tid":2205222,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"民營企業要建立黨支部，加強員工思想建設<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坚持政治标准，积极稳妥做好在民营经济代表人士优秀分子中发展党员工作，把政治素质好、群众认可度高、符合党员条件的民营经济代表人士及时吸收到党内来。所在单位没有党组织的，县级以上党委（党组）组织人事部门可直接做好联系培养工作。<br />\n唔知個人入左黨份身家駛唔駛都入埋黨呢?"},{"pid":"c6a32e82e8a84bc63e2b6b170fc0c7b3aa7eb4ea","tid":2205222,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"同志们￼￼￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cae795b76bbfddc31dc1424435b83d09e99e3e","tid":2205222,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}